<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <h2><span>#</span> about-me</h2>
      <div class="section-head-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text reveal" style="transition-delay:0.1s">
        <p>
          <strong>Hello, I'm Raihan Niloy.</strong> I'm a full-stack software engineer with 7+ years of professional experience building enterprise software at Dynamic Solutions Innovators Ltd. — from ERP integrations to government-grade platforms to machine learning systems.
        </p>
        <p>
          My stack spans Java, Python, and JavaScript. I'm equally comfortable architecting backend systems, designing ETL pipelines, or diving into ML-powered document processing. I graduated in Computer Science from Mawlana Bhashani Science and Technology University in 2017.
        </p>
        <p>
          Outside of work, I tinker with open-source tools and build utilities I wish existed — like <strong>Alchemy_Analytics</strong> (a visual SQL query builder) and <strong>tinkerbd</strong> (an e-commerce website for my business).
        </p>
        <div class="about-facts">
          <div class="fact-tag">Java</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">Spring Boot</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">Python</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">TypeScript</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">Oracle</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">SQL</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">PyTorch</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">Apache Superset</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">ETL</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">NLP</div>
          <div class="fact-tag">Bangladesh 🇧🇩</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-photo-wrap reveal" style="transition-delay:0.25s">
        <!-- To add your photo: replace the .about-photo div with:
             <img src="/your-photo.jpg" alt="Raihan Niloy" style="width:100%;border:1px solid var(--border)" />
        -->
        <div class="about-photo">
          <div class="about-photo-corner tl"></div>
          <div class="about-photo-corner tr"></div>
          <div class="about-photo-corner bl"></div>
